data.description: Beautiful, move in ready 2 story Cape Cod on a full walk-up basement. Generously sized rooms with lots of storage space.  Eat in kitchen with island, separate dining room/office, beautiful original hardwood floors.  New roof, updated windows. This home has two fireplaces; one gas in living room and a wood burning fireplace in the basement family room.  The basement also has a room currently being used as a 5th bedroom. Great location, located on a cud-de-sac with nice established landscaping.  Fenced in yard, storage building. Large deck that leads to a nice big backyard. Much more! As Is, however inspections are welcome.
